name: UFbxAssetImportData
doc: Base class for import data and options used when importing any asset from FBX

bConvertScene: Convert the scene from FBX coordinate system to UE coordinate system
bForceFrontXAxis: Convert the scene from FBX coordinate system to UE coordinate system with front X axis instead of -Y
bConvertSceneUnit: Convert the scene from FBX unit to UE unit (centimeter).
